'''PeerStream''' (formerly '''SNAP Interactive''') is an [[United States| American]] [[computer software]]<ref>[https://techcrunch.com/2011/01/14/snap-interactive-raises-8-5-million-for-social-dating-applications/ "SNAP Interactive Raises $8.5 Million For Social Dating Applications"] ''Tech Crunch''. Retrieved 2014-5-2.</ref><ref>[http://seekingalpha.com/article/331542-snap-interactive-facebooks-fast-growing-and-most-undervalued-social-media-company "Snap Interactive: Facebook's Fast Growing And Most Undervalued Social Media Company"] ''Seeking Alpha''. Retrieved 2014-5-2.</ref>

On March 12, 2018, Snap Interactive, Inc. rebranded to PeerStream, Inc.(OTCQB:PEER). PeerStream is a developer of decentralized technologies for multimedia social apps and business communication.<ref>[https://www.peerstream.com/snap-interactive-announces-corporate-name-change-to-peerstream-and-formation-of-new-business-solutions-unit-2/] ''March 12, 2018 Press Release''. Retrieved 2017-3-12.</ref>

